    "the_philosophy": "95% accuracy requires a paradigm shift from 'let winners run' to 'take profit immediately at first sign of profit and never let a trade reverse.' Each trade is targetting +1-2% with near-certainty, not +10% with 60% probability.",
    "the_tradeoff": "Average P&L drops from +1.37% (V3) to ~+1.1% (V5). But compounding is dramatically better with 1/4 the drawdown and near-zero probability of consecutive losers.",
